definitions.definition: Any of many types of stinging flying insect resembling a hornet .
( entomology ) Any of the members of suborder Apocrita , excepting the ants (family Formicidae ) and bees (clade Anthophila ).

subdefinitions.definition: Any of the members of the family Vespidae .

definitions.definition: A person who behaves in an angry or insolent way, hence waspishly .

main_definition: Any of many types of stinging flying insect resembling a hornet .
